text: Hi there! Does someone have a workaround for the fact that <https://sub.domain.com/hs/scriptloader/YOURHUBID.js> isn't minified by HubSpot? Thanks!
<@U6TBZ66FN> was this the file that was on the staging or dev and being tested?
HubSpot knows of a few files that aren't minified and are throwing errors in stuff like PageSpeed, SEMRush, Moz and more. I believe they are working towards making them minified
It should be minified in the subsequent request — the minification happens at CDN. Let know if it is still not minified — I can take a look at the URL.
